  <thing id="spNNWCrNos" name="Create Nosferatu" description="When cast on a corpse, or over a grave, this spell causes its target to rise as a Nosferatu vampire. The transformation begins immediately, but is not complete until the next new moon, when the corpse will awaken and begin preying upon the living. The Nosferatu is under no obligation to obey the raster in any way, and acts as it chooses. Furthermore, the spell does not actually restore the spirit of the deceased to their body. Instead, it allows the spirit of a malevolent fiend to enter the body. This fiend controls all the corpse&apos;s actions, and is a completely separate person from the deceased, with its own sinister goals, plans, and memories. Fiends that become Nosferatu in this manner are universally malicious and evil." compset="Spell">
