  <thing id="abNNWCOSUV" name="Sunlight Vulnerabitiy" description="When a culled one is exposed to direct sunlight, their skin begins to glow a brilliant golden color. This effect imposes a -40 penalty on Stealth checks and outlines the culled one even if he is invisible. \n\nFurther, culled ones are dazzled as long as they are exposed to sunlight." compset="Ability" summary="-40 penalty on Stealth checks &amp; Dazzled">
