  <thing id="fNNWVmpSns" name="Vampiric Senses" description="{b}Benefit{/b}: As a swift action, by spending 1 blood point, you can gain an enhancement bonus on all Perception and Sense Motive checks, as well as on all Survival checks made to spot or follow tracks, equal to 10 + your cruomancer level. This benefit lasts for 1 min./level.\n\nIf your cruomancer level is 6 or higher, you can activate this ability by spending only a single blood point." compset="Feat" summary="Heighten your senses, sharpening them beyond any mortal&apos;s." uniqueness="useronce">
    <fieldval field="actName" value="10 + Cruomancer level skill bonus"/>
