  <thing id="raNNWUncHn" name="Uncontrollable Hunger" description="Each day, a starving feral vampire must succeed on a Will save (DC 15 + 1 per day since it became starving) or else immediately set out in search of a sentient creature to kill and consume. It will avoid obvious and unnecessary peril (not, for instance, jumping into a nearby stream in search of aquatic prey) but must otherwise do everything in its power to satiate its hunger." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Will save (DC 15 + 1 per day) or set out in search of prey" uniqueness="useronce">
