  <thing id="raNNWHngQu" name="Quadruped" description="A starving feral vampire&apos;s hands transform fully into claws and its arms into forelimbs. Starving feral vampires cannot hold things with their hands, and cannot do anything that requires hands for fine manipulation. Additionally, starving feral vampires are four-legged, granting a +4 bonus to CMD for the purposes of trip attempts. The feral vampire can still use its claws to make attacks." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Hands transform fully into claws and its arms into forelimbs">
