  <thing id="cRevCruoma" name="Cruomancy" description="For each level of revenant that a character gains, her cruomancer level increases by 1. Additionally, as she gains additional levels of revenant, the maximum number of blood points that she can have in her blood point pool increases, as indicated on the class table." compset="ClSpecial" summary="For each level gained, your cruomancer level increases by 1">
