  <thing id="cNN1lifeli" name="Life Like" description="Beginning at 1st level, a revenant infiltrator adds 1/2 her level to Diplomacy checks made to influence the attitudes of humanoid creatures, as well as to Disguise checks made to appear as a living creature (minimum +1)." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Diplomacy checks to influence the attitudes of humanoid creatures">
