field[abValue].value += maximum(round(bonu2,0,-1),1)

field[livename].text = "Life Like: Bonus + " & field[abValue].value & ""]]></eval>
    </thing>
  <thing id="cNN1parstr" name="Paralyzing Strike" description="Beginning at 1st level, a revenant infiltrator learns how to strike a foe in such a way as to leave them paralyzed. As a standard action, the revenant\ninfiltrator can make a single melee attack against a creature. If the attack hits, it deals damage as normal, and the target must succeed on a Fortitude save (DC 10 + 1/2 the revenant infiltrator’s class level + the revenant infiltrator’s Intelligence modifier) or be paralyzed. The target may make a new saving\nthrow each round as a full-round action to end the effect, but all saving throws after the first suffer a -4 penalty. Even if the target is unable to succeed on any saving throws, the effect ends automatically after 5 minutes. If the attack misses, the use of the ability is wasted. Creatures that are not living (such\nas constructs or undead), or are immune to critical hits or precision-based damage, are immune to this ability.\n\nThe revenant infiltrator can use this ability once per day at 1st level. At 5th level, and every four levels thereafter, she can use this ability one additional time per day." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Strike a foe in such a way as to leave them paralyzed">
