  <thing id="cNN1lswkns" name="Lose Weakness" description="At 3rd level, and every four levels thereafter, a revenant infiltrator may choose a single lesser weakness that she gained as a result of gaining the revenant\ntemplate, and lose it, forever freeing herself of that particular weakness. Beginning at 15th level, she can choose to lose a single greater weakness, rather than a single lesser weakness, each time that she gains this ability. The revenant cannot lose the blood dependency or sunlight vulnerability weaknesses in this way." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Remove a single weakness">
